{"data":[{"name":"84:1","price":"当天绽裂，","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنشَقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5885,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:2","price":"听从其养主之命，而且宜于听从的时候；","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5886,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:3","price":"当地展开，","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡأَرۡضُ مُدَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5887,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:4","price":"并抛其所怀，而且变为空虚，","arabic":"وَأَلۡقَتۡ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5888,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:5","price":"听从其养主之命，而且宜于听从的时候；","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5889,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:6","price":"人啊！你必定勉力工作，直到会见你的养主，你将看到自己的劳绩。","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدۡحٗا فَمُلَٰقِيهِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5890,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:7","price":"至于用右手接过自己的功过簿者，","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5891,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:8","price":"将受简易的稽核，","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابٗا يَسِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5892,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:9","price":"而兴高采烈地返于他的家属；","arabic":"وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5893,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:10","price":"至于从背后接受自己的功过簿者，","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهۡرِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5894,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:11","price":"将叫苦连天，","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يَدۡعُواْ ثُبُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5895,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:12","price":"入于烈火之中，","arabic":"وَيَصۡلَىٰ سَعِيرًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5896,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:13","price":"从前他在家属间原是快乐的，","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِيٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5897,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:14","price":"他已猜想他绝不会归于主。","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5898,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:15","price":"不然，他的养主，原是鉴察他的。","arabic":"بَلَىٰٓۚ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5899,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:16","price":"我以晚霞盟誓，","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلشَّفَقِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5900,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:17","price":"以黑夜及其包罗万象的盟誓，","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5901,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:18","price":"以圆满时的月亮盟誓，","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا ٱتَّسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5902,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:19","price":"你们必定遭遇重重的灾难。","arabic":"لَتَرۡكَبُنَّ طَبَقًا عَن طَبَقٖ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5903,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:20","price":"他们怎能不归信呢？","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُمۡ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5904,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:21","price":"当别人对他们宣读《古兰经》的时候，他们怎么不叩头呢？۩","arabic":"وَإِذَا قُرِئَ عَلَيۡهِمُ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ لَا يَسۡجُدُونَۤ۩","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5905,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:22","price":"不然，不归信的人们，是否认〔真理〕的，","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ يُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5906,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:23","price":"安拉全知道他们心中隐藏的东西，","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَا يُوعُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5907,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:24","price":"故你当以一种痛苦的刑罚向他们报喜，","arabic":"فَبَشِّرۡهُم بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5908,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"84:25","price":"惟归信而且行善的人们，将受不断的报酬。","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ أَجۡرٌ غَيۡرُ مَمۡنُونِۭ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5909,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq","Chapter Al-Inshiqaq","Inshiqaq","Surah Inshiqaq","Chapter Inshiqaq","Al Inshiqaq","Surah Al Inshiqaq","Chapter Al Inshiqaq","Surah 84","Chapter 84","The Splitting Open","الإنشقاق"]}